FBIS3-57037 "drsov015_r_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-015 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Jan 1994 Azerbaijan Azeri Troops Renew Offensive LD2201121194 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1100 GMT 22 Jan 94 LD2201121194 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] This morning, after intense rocket and artillery preparation, Azerbaijani troops renewed their offensive in the north of the Nagorno-Karabakh Mardakertskiy rayon. The LUR agency reports that, as of 1200, the Nagorno-Karabakh defensive forces are managing to check the enemy's advance. According to the information available, the Azerbaijani army has sustained serious losses in men and equipment. Intense firing from fixed positions is going on in other sectors of the front.
